title: How to Become Self-Aware And Unlock Your True Potential, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO169
itunes:title: How to Become Self-Aware And Unlock Your True Potential, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO169
description: How have I worked through the process of building something successful? How have I developed the mindset that has helped me earn millions of dollars? I've tried different kinds of life hacks and mental tools over the years. One thing that I really believe in is holding yourself accountable. How do you do that? In this podcast, I share two practical tools - a set of questions and a mental dialogue - that have helped me immensely. Listen to find out what they are.
